name: kvin-nb
docker_compose_file:
services:
  jupyter:
    image: quay.io/jupyter/base-notebook
    user: root
    environment:
      - GRANT_SUDO=yes
    ports:
      - "8888:8888"
    volumes:
      - /:/host/
      - /var/run/tappd.sock:/var/run/tappd.sock
      - /var/run/dstack.sock:/var/run/dstack.sock
    logging:
      driver: journald
      options:
        tag: jupyter-notebook
